      "_value": "Look for #p103# in #m10000000#."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "In #m10000000#, I met Jane, a girl wearing bunny ears. #p103# says she wants to travel the world, but her dad won't let her. She thinks if I get her #b15 #t4000016#s and 15 #t04000019#s#k, her father will change his mind."
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I delivered the #b#t4000016#s and #t04000019#s#k to #p103#. I wonder if this will really change her father's mind... she's wearing bunny ears, for goodness sake! Ah well, it's none of my business. In return, Jane gave me a Scroll for ATT. My weapon's going to be awesome... if the scroll works."
    },
