  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "My dream is to travel freely around the world, just like you! But, argh, my dad won't let me. I tell him I'm ready to spread my wings a little, but he just won't listen."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hmm. You look pretty strong. Can... can I ask you a favor? Please defeat #r30 #o16#s and #o19#s#k, and collect #b15 #t4000016#s#k and #b15 #t4000019#s#k. If you can do this for me, my father might give me permission to travel the world. Please, I'm begging you..."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirName": "2",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "A #t4000016# looks like #i4000016# and a #t4000019# looks like #i4000019#. You can get them from #o16#s and #o19#s. Oooh, I'm so excited about this!"
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Incredible! You defeated so many #o16#s and #o19#s! Now I can prove to my dad that I'm strong enough to travel by myself! Hehehe! What? It's not dishonest... I could've done it on my own, but I didn't want to leave town behind my dad's back..."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "It's none of your business anyway. Here, just take your reward and don't ask so many questions."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "This scroll can strengthen a certain weapon. Just open the Use tab of your Item Inventory and open your Equipment Inventory at the same time, then drag the scroll onto the weapon. There's a chance the scroll will fail, but life's risky like that..."
        }
      },
